<https://www.gov.uk/government/people/mark-hunt> <http://ogp.me/ns#description> "Air Vice-Marshal Mark Hunt was appointed Deputy Director General and Technical Director for the Defence Safety Authority on 18 December 2024. His previous Ministry of Defence roles include: Defence Equipment and Support Team Leader, Type Airworthiness Authority, Portfolio Head and Principal Engineer Director of Ground Training (delivering the RAF’s education policy, governance and assurance for all 27 specialist disciplines) Deputy Air Officer commanding No 22 Group Commandant of the Defence School of Aeronautical Engineering RAF Cosford’s Station Commander, Head of Establishment and Accountable Manager Chief Air Engineer at RAF Brize Norton"@en <https://forgetmenot.local/extractor/rdfa> .
